              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-[4px]">
              <p class="text-[length:var(--font-size-xl)] font-[number:var(--font-body-bold-weight)] leading-[140%] tracking-[-0.04em] text-[color:var(--ploy-text-primary)]">
                @ads spotted a traffic anomaly on /pricing
